@koushik-das Github cannot display large diffs. This is how you can show it on your local checkout:

```
prId=1277
git checkout master
git fetch origin pull/${prId}/head:pr/${prId}
git checkout pr/${prId}
git show 2aab4c142d47b77e7bbc584927a80b8ba180934e engine/orchestration/src/org/apache/cloudstack/engine/orchestration/NetworkOrchestrator.java
```

Hope this helps.

Nice work guys!

